WEBVTT

01:39.330 --> 01:43.560
[Road to Success]

01:44.630 --> 01:47.890
[Episode 8]

02:16.770 --> 02:18.930
Why is there a hole in your shoe?

02:26.520 --> 02:27.430
Sit down.

02:28.190 --> 02:29.150
Take them off.

02:29.630 --> 02:30.590
Go on.

02:36.520 --> 02:37.440
Here.

02:37.640 --> 02:38.310
Put them on.

02:38.310 --> 02:39.800
I'm being discharged soon.

02:39.800 --> 02:41.280
Consider it a gift.

02:43.780 --> 02:45.000
You gave me a gift,

02:45.000 --> 02:46.530
but I don't have money to buy you one.

02:46.530 --> 02:48.900
Then buy me one when we grow up.

02:49.000 --> 02:51.030
Okay, then you can
help me put the shoes on too.

02:51.030 --> 02:51.840
Okay.

02:53.280 --> 02:55.079
They don't look like them at all.

02:55.520 --> 02:57.720
No wonder you couldn't recognize them.

03:12.190 --> 03:13.500
How do you say "Jia She" in English?

03:13.500 --> 03:14.520
Hypothesis.

03:14.540 --> 03:15.330
Spell it.

03:16.870 --> 03:19.470
H-y-p-o-t-h-e-s-i-s.

03:19.470 --> 03:20.400
Good, good.

03:20.400 --> 03:23.470
What is the difference between
"hypothesis" and "theory"?

03:23.470 --> 03:24.470
One is

03:25.910 --> 03:27.400
an unverified guess.

03:27.400 --> 03:29.190
The other is a proven fact.

03:29.190 --> 03:31.010
Very good. Eat.

03:31.190 --> 03:32.110
No eat.

03:33.120 --> 03:34.910
Modal verbs for speculation.

03:37.190 --> 03:38.720
Affirmative speculation.

03:39.400 --> 03:40.280
You don't know?

03:42.400 --> 03:45.190
"Must have done." Read it 3 times!

03:45.190 --> 03:46.450
Otherwise, don't eat.

03:47.190 --> 03:50.030
Too... many... people.

03:50.030 --> 03:51.360
Must have done!

03:51.360 --> 03:52.910
Must have done!

03:55.000 --> 03:56.620
Must have done!

03:56.640 --> 03:58.280
Must have done!

03:58.590 --> 03:59.800
Must have done!

03:59.800 --> 04:00.400
One more time!

04:00.400 --> 04:01.590
Must have done!

04:01.590 --> 04:02.120
One more time!

04:02.120 --> 04:03.680
Must have done!

04:03.680 --> 04:04.720
Okay, okay.

04:04.750 --> 04:06.710
-Eat.
-Eat, eat.

04:09.800 --> 04:10.280
Hello.

04:14.960 --> 04:15.840
Ms. Lin!

04:20.070 --> 04:22.200
How is the team's condition recently?

04:22.360 --> 04:23.160
Pretty good.

04:24.240 --> 04:25.050
Have they...

04:25.240 --> 04:26.940
been acting a bit abnormal?

04:27.390 --> 04:29.920
You must pay attention
to their mental state.

04:32.470 --> 04:34.070
Don't worry, Director Qian.

04:36.080 --> 04:36.880
I won't worry.

04:39.000 --> 04:41.300
"Over a long period of time
in the future."

04:41.300 --> 04:42.510
"In the long run!"

04:43.800 --> 04:45.270
In the long run!

04:46.800 --> 04:48.120
"To have no more of something left."

04:48.120 --> 04:49.750
"Run out of!"

04:50.159 --> 04:51.630
Run out of!

04:53.830 --> 04:55.720
"To think someone is less important
or not as good as you."

04:55.720 --> 04:57.240
"Look down on!"

04:57.240 --> 04:58.600
Look down on? You sure?

04:59.240 --> 05:01.330
I look down on you!

05:01.430 --> 05:03.390
-And you!
-I...

05:03.390 --> 05:04.680
-You!
-You! Not me!

05:04.680 --> 05:08.190
-You, you, you!
-You, you, you!

05:08.190 --> 05:09.870
You, you, you!

05:09.870 --> 05:12.190
Come on, be patient! Me!

05:13.000 --> 05:13.800
Patient!

05:15.480 --> 05:17.120
The show is wonderful,

05:17.120 --> 05:18.300
but Coach Wang Fa,

05:18.510 --> 05:20.570
it seems you should go coach them now.

05:21.120 --> 05:22.000
No rush.

05:22.830 --> 05:25.870
After all, watching a talk show outside
is quite expensive.

05:25.870 --> 05:27.120
You, you, you!

05:29.680 --> 05:31.800
This Qin Ao is really hopeless.

05:32.830 --> 05:33.950
This won't work.

05:33.980 --> 05:36.170
I will give his cards to Lin Lu.

05:45.240 --> 05:46.720
Get along with!

05:48.000 --> 05:49.600
Get along with!

05:51.830 --> 05:53.270
Make friends with!

05:54.040 --> 05:55.720
Make friends with!

05:57.120 --> 05:58.680
Fall in love with!

05:58.680 --> 06:01.040
Fall in love with!

06:05.090 --> 06:10.190
Invigilators, please unseal
and distribute the test papers.

06:05.130 --> 06:07.350
[One Week Later]

06:10.190 --> 06:14.000
Instruct students
to fill in their personal information

06:14.000 --> 06:17.560
and paste their barcodes.

06:21.040 --> 06:22.210
Everyone,

06:22.360 --> 06:24.240
please comply with
the examination room regulations.

06:24.240 --> 06:26.370
We'll distribute the test papers now.

07:32.130 --> 07:33.570
[Monthly English Exam Paper
for Senior Year, First Semester]

07:41.690 --> 07:44.550
[Monthly English Exam Paper
for Senior Year, First Semester]

08:12.800 --> 08:13.920
Sir.

08:13.920 --> 08:14.680
Well...

08:15.120 --> 08:16.230
I need to go to the toilet.

08:16.230 --> 08:18.490
Go ahead. Don't disturb other students.

09:14.800 --> 09:15.680
Fu.

09:19.480 --> 09:22.120
Aren't we about the same level?

09:22.120 --> 09:24.650
Why did you
take that English tutoring class?

09:26.270 --> 09:31.580
[Class 7, Grade 12]

09:36.720 --> 09:38.120
Did I screw up the test?

09:43.960 --> 09:45.220
Who said that?

09:49.240 --> 09:50.100
What happened?

09:50.360 --> 09:52.910
You scored 0.5 points
higher than Wen Chengye!

09:52.910 --> 09:53.490
Really?

09:53.510 --> 09:54.710
-Of course!
-Really!

09:55.670 --> 09:57.000
Good job!

09:57.440 --> 09:58.550
0.5...

09:58.370 --> 09:59.330
[Class 7, Grade 12]

09:59.600 --> 10:00.330
Wen Chengye!

10:04.630 --> 10:05.890
Let's get reacquainted.

10:05.890 --> 10:08.500
I'm Fu Xinshu, midfielder of
the No. 8 High School football team, No. 10.

10:08.500 --> 10:10.110
[Class 7, Grade 12]

10:08.550 --> 10:09.680
Welcome to the team.

10:21.630 --> 10:22.480
Fu Xinshu!

10:24.910 --> 10:27.310
Director Jin
wants to see you in his office.

10:30.480 --> 10:30.960
Okay.

10:34.630 --> 10:37.290
What is Jin Laoyao up to this time?

10:37.390 --> 10:39.380
It's fine. I'll go with you.

10:39.480 --> 10:40.240
Let's go.

10:40.240 --> 10:41.840
It's never good news when he looks for me.

10:41.840 --> 10:43.780
I really, really don't want to see him.

10:43.780 --> 10:44.910
You don't want to see him.

10:44.910 --> 10:46.080
Me neither.

10:49.660 --> 10:52.720
[Monthly English Exam Paper
for Senior Year, First Semester]

10:50.120 --> 10:50.630
This

10:50.630 --> 10:52.360
is Fu's paper from the last monthly exam.

10:52.360 --> 10:53.320
77 points.

10:53.550 --> 10:54.440
And this

10:54.440 --> 10:56.630
is Fu's paper from this exam.

10:55.140 --> 10:56.530
[Monthly English Exam Paper
for Senior Year, First Semester]

10:56.660 --> 10:58.200
123.5 points.

10:58.200 --> 10:59.630
Only a month has passed,

10:59.630 --> 11:00.870
and his score changed too much.

11:00.870 --> 11:01.600
I need to verify it.

11:01.600 --> 11:02.870
It's not impossible.

11:03.870 --> 11:04.750
Director Jin!

11:05.390 --> 11:06.320
I can prove

11:06.320 --> 11:07.520
that he didn't cheat.

11:10.510 --> 11:11.390
Director Jin.

11:11.390 --> 11:13.000
The members of our football team have been

11:13.000 --> 11:14.360
studying English very hard together.

11:14.360 --> 11:15.820
I taught them the methods.

11:16.360 --> 11:17.400
Ms. Lin,

11:17.510 --> 11:19.270
I need to understand the situation.

11:19.270 --> 11:20.720
They never studied hard before,

11:20.720 --> 11:22.510
and they're suddenly working hard now?

11:22.510 --> 11:23.440
What do you mean?

11:23.440 --> 11:25.040
You really don't believe us?

11:28.630 --> 11:30.230
My words might be a bit harsh.

11:30.600 --> 11:32.360
But haven't you caused enough trouble?

11:32.360 --> 11:33.320
Other things aside,

11:33.320 --> 11:36.120
cheating and lying
are absolutely unacceptable.

11:37.080 --> 11:37.840
I didn't cheat.

11:37.840 --> 11:39.440
And they didn't lie either.

11:39.440 --> 11:40.360
Isn't there surveillance in the exam room?

11:40.360 --> 11:41.960
You can check it.

11:42.240 --> 11:43.030
I'd like to check too.

11:43.030 --> 11:44.600
But it happens that the camera
in your exam room is broken.

11:44.600 --> 11:45.200
So I can't.

11:45.200 --> 11:45.870
Director Jin.

11:45.870 --> 11:47.000
Even in court,

11:47.000 --> 11:47.720
without evidence,

11:47.720 --> 11:49.240
one is presumed innocent.

11:49.240 --> 11:51.200
How can you jump to conclusions so easily?

11:51.200 --> 11:52.440
You have to understand the school.

11:52.440 --> 11:53.440
For the sake of fairness,

11:53.440 --> 11:55.240
this score must be invalidated.

12:00.030 --> 12:01.240
If I can prove

12:01.240 --> 12:02.840
that Fu Xinshu didn't cheat,

12:03.000 --> 12:04.460
will you apologize to him?

12:08.240 --> 12:09.840
How are you going to prove it?

12:10.790 --> 12:12.200
Every time the school sets an exam,

12:12.200 --> 12:13.390
they make two sets, A and B,

12:13.390 --> 12:15.730
with the same difficulty and coverage.

12:15.870 --> 12:17.080
You can get paper B

12:17.080 --> 12:18.030
and let him do it on the spot.

12:18.030 --> 12:18.910
Okay.

12:19.120 --> 12:20.150
Do it on the spot.

12:56.330 --> 12:58.380
128!

12:58.840 --> 13:00.510
-Yes!
-Yes!

13:14.000 --> 13:15.130
Look, Director Jin.

13:24.910 --> 13:25.710
Director Jin.

13:26.440 --> 13:29.440
You still remember
what you promised earlier, right?

13:51.390 --> 13:52.630
I'm sorry, Fu.

13:53.600 --> 13:55.240
We'll record your score
as 128 for this exam.

13:55.240 --> 13:55.750
No need.

13:56.630 --> 13:57.910
Just keep it at 123.5.

13:58.750 --> 14:00.510
This is the actual score

14:00.510 --> 14:02.040
I earned myself in the exam.

14:06.240 --> 14:07.120
Alright then.

14:07.720 --> 14:08.840
Thank you, Ms. Lin.

14:13.670 --> 14:15.080
Alright, everyone dismiss.

14:15.080 --> 14:16.070
Go back to class.

14:16.200 --> 14:18.200
-Go now. Go back to class.
-Let's go.

14:19.390 --> 14:20.670
Thank you, Director Jin.

14:20.670 --> 14:21.550
Thank you.

14:27.550 --> 14:29.870
-Well done. You're a straight A student now.
-Fu.

14:29.870 --> 14:30.600
128.

14:30.600 --> 14:32.600
-Not bad.
-How do you feel now?

14:32.600 --> 14:33.390
Good job.

14:33.390 --> 14:34.150
-Come on, Boss.
-Not bad, huh?

14:34.150 --> 14:34.910
Why are you crying?

14:34.910 --> 14:35.750
Not bad.

14:36.240 --> 14:37.580
You know what?

14:37.750 --> 14:39.150
Your daddy is happy.

14:41.390 --> 14:42.260
Fu.

14:42.750 --> 14:44.550
We can consider this a win for us.

14:45.440 --> 14:46.500
My son has grown up.

14:47.540 --> 14:49.240
Alright, alright.

14:50.000 --> 14:50.750
Win!

14:50.750 --> 14:52.120
We're Mr. Win!

14:53.390 --> 14:55.170
Win! Win! Win!

14:55.190 --> 14:56.990
Win! Win! Win!

14:57.010 --> 14:59.630
Win! Win! Win!

15:00.030 --> 15:01.520
-Ms. Lin.
-Hello, Ms. Lin.

15:01.550 --> 15:02.510
Ms. Lin.

15:03.790 --> 15:04.550
Ms. Lin,

15:05.120 --> 15:06.270
if you give me a drop,

15:06.270 --> 15:08.110
I'll repay you with a fountain.

15:08.110 --> 15:09.030
-What?
-What?

15:09.030 --> 15:10.800
What did you say?

15:10.960 --> 15:12.620
You guys don't even know this?

15:12.870 --> 15:13.790
A drop of kindness

15:13.790 --> 15:15.390
deserves a spring in return.

15:17.910 --> 15:20.630
if you give me a drop,

15:20.630 --> 15:23.390
I'll repay you with a fountain!

15:23.590 --> 15:24.500
♪ The night sky and starlight ♪

15:25.230 --> 15:29.680
♪ Secret words falling into my palm ♪

15:29.270 --> 15:31.030
Don't tell anyone outside
that I taught you English.

15:30.520 --> 15:32.500
♪ Unraveling the mystery ♪

15:33.240 --> 15:35.630
-Let's go.
-Let's go. Let's go.

15:33.380 --> 15:36.610
♪ It was you who gave me this brilliance ♪

15:36.000 --> 15:36.910
Then I won't eat it.

15:36.910 --> 15:38.270
I definitely won't eat the food you grill.

15:38.270 --> 15:39.630
We must reward Fu with some meat.

15:38.570 --> 15:43.810
♪ The distance
that brings our dreams closer ♪

15:41.630 --> 15:42.790
Of course there is.

15:42.790 --> 15:44.390
Didn't expect that, did you?

15:45.130 --> 15:45.970
♪ To run toward you ♪

15:46.120 --> 15:51.070
♪ I keep practicing with no turning back ♪

15:54.700 --> 15:55.860
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

15:57.110 --> 15:58.520
♪ Because you're with me ♪

16:00.710 --> 16:04.320
[Academic Building]

16:01.350 --> 16:02.660
♪ The light shimmers ♪

16:04.050 --> 16:05.250
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

16:06.960 --> 16:07.980
♪ Running towards you ♪

16:08.980 --> 16:10.170
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

16:14.020 --> 16:14.880
♪ Walk side by side ♪

16:15.820 --> 16:17.690
♪ Become ourselves ♪

16:22.240 --> 16:23.000
Wen Chengye.

16:29.510 --> 16:31.000
The cheat sheet Qin Ao made for you.

16:31.000 --> 16:32.550
I saw it and picked it up.

16:34.720 --> 16:35.200
I...

16:39.790 --> 16:40.270
Come on.

16:40.790 --> 16:42.630
Seriously, Wen Chengye.
Don't be like this.

16:42.630 --> 16:44.510
Qin Ao probably just wanted to help me.

16:44.510 --> 16:46.550
Please don't
make things difficult for him.

16:46.550 --> 16:48.080
You were very focused during the exam

16:48.080 --> 16:49.080
and didn't see it.

16:52.480 --> 16:53.240
Fu Xinshu.

16:56.480 --> 16:57.360
You won.

17:01.620 --> 17:03.580
[IT Center]

17:15.240 --> 17:15.839
Of course,

17:16.200 --> 17:17.790
you can't compare to this.

17:19.480 --> 17:20.640
Stop complaining.

17:20.640 --> 17:21.750
Just practice hard.

17:21.750 --> 17:23.950
I wonder if Wen Chengye will come today.

17:28.550 --> 17:29.400
Let me tell you,

17:29.400 --> 17:31.270
Wen Chengye won't come.

17:31.270 --> 17:32.500
If he comes,

17:33.110 --> 17:34.710
I'll write my name backward.

17:35.750 --> 17:37.640
It might not be a good thing
even if he comes.

17:37.640 --> 17:38.920
If he comes, I'll beat him up.

17:38.920 --> 17:41.110
Beating someone like him won't help,

17:41.130 --> 17:42.790
unless you beat him on the court.

17:42.790 --> 17:44.000
Yeah, Boss.

17:44.000 --> 17:45.200
Don't speak too soon.

17:46.880 --> 17:47.640
How about this?

17:47.640 --> 17:48.750
If he comes,

17:48.750 --> 17:50.920
Chen Jianghe and I
will ride a bike together for you to see.

17:50.920 --> 17:51.780
How about that?

17:53.000 --> 17:53.830
How about it?

17:55.880 --> 17:56.740
Say something.

17:57.480 --> 17:58.810
Isn't that Wen Chengye?

17:59.400 --> 18:00.160
Where?

18:01.480 --> 18:02.480
Right next to you.

18:04.750 --> 18:05.160
Qin Ao.

18:05.160 --> 18:06.440
Watch your mouth.

18:06.440 --> 18:08.440
If you don't know how to use it properly,
I'll rip it off.

18:08.440 --> 18:10.100
How would I know? How would...

18:10.720 --> 18:11.810
Coach is here.

18:20.790 --> 18:21.360
Come on.

18:21.640 --> 18:23.160
After 10 minutes of warm-up,

18:23.160 --> 18:25.820
we'll do one-on-two
breakthrough and defense practice.

18:25.820 --> 18:26.980
Got it, Coach.

18:27.110 --> 18:28.640
-Let's go.
-Start!

18:28.790 --> 18:30.320
-Okay.
-Alright. Let's go.

18:32.790 --> 18:35.390
Wen Chengye
is getting more and more arrogant.

18:36.400 --> 18:37.830
I really can't stand him.

18:41.550 --> 18:43.070
What's the use of him being arrogant now?

18:43.070 --> 18:45.200
Let's see what he's really made of.

18:47.310 --> 18:49.570
Shouldn't you be snapping back at me now?

18:49.680 --> 18:50.880
Are you asking for it?

18:53.480 --> 18:54.160
Coach.

18:55.480 --> 18:56.590
I'll team up with Chen Jianghe

18:56.590 --> 18:58.120
to guard Wen Chengye first.

19:01.960 --> 19:03.090
I'll team up with Fu.

19:06.110 --> 19:07.040
Let's crush him.

19:11.720 --> 19:13.310
Block him! Block him!

19:14.240 --> 19:14.920
Defend!

19:29.230 --> 19:30.780
Is this all you two got?

19:33.960 --> 19:36.070
Boss, I'll avenge you!

19:36.070 --> 19:37.830
-Go, Lu!
-Go for it!

19:37.830 --> 19:38.930
-Go! Go!
-Let's do it together!

19:38.930 --> 19:40.210
Keep your man!

20:19.070 --> 20:20.110
Come on.

20:20.850 --> 20:21.960
Come on!

20:30.430 --> 20:32.020
I can't watch this anymore. Let's go.

20:32.020 --> 20:33.160
Come on.

20:33.160 --> 20:33.920
Let me teach you another lesson.

20:33.920 --> 20:35.320
Stop looking at the ball.

20:47.640 --> 20:48.310
Of course.

20:48.310 --> 20:50.240
Offense always has the advantage.

20:51.550 --> 20:54.810
It would be the same if I was on offense
and he was on defense.

20:56.070 --> 20:57.310
Come on. Those two

20:57.310 --> 20:58.920
in front blocked my way.

20:59.160 --> 21:00.160
Right.

21:00.830 --> 21:02.290
What were you guys saying?

21:02.960 --> 21:04.110
If I come,

21:05.030 --> 21:06.890
you two will ride a bike together?

21:11.140 --> 21:11.940
It's fine.

21:13.160 --> 21:15.160
As long as you admit you're a coward.

21:17.400 --> 21:18.130
Wen Chengye.

21:30.590 --> 21:31.440
Alright.

21:32.980 --> 21:36.740
Let's just give him a welcome ceremony.

21:41.400 --> 21:42.200
Let me see.

21:48.080 --> 21:50.450
-Get on.
-Let's go.

21:51.590 --> 21:52.680
I have to pedal first, right?

21:52.680 --> 21:53.550
Can you do it?

21:53.550 --> 21:54.400
You pedal first?

21:54.400 --> 21:56.160
-I pedal first!
-What do you mean by that?

21:56.160 --> 21:56.590
It must be me.

21:56.590 --> 21:58.550
If you pedal first,
we won't be able to ride.

21:58.550 --> 21:59.750
Let me do it.

21:59.750 --> 22:01.160
-I'm pedaling.
-Come on!

22:01.160 --> 22:01.960
Aren't I supposed to pedal?

22:01.960 --> 22:04.400
How can you do it if you start directly?

22:06.790 --> 22:07.960
Pedal first! Pedal!

22:07.960 --> 22:09.680
-Chen Jianghe.
-Let me give you a push.

22:09.680 --> 22:10.680
Come on, go.

22:10.680 --> 22:12.590
Three, two, one, go!

22:18.110 --> 22:19.240
Don't fly off, you two.

22:19.240 --> 22:20.090
Speed up!

22:21.160 --> 22:23.070
You pedal! Go!

22:27.830 --> 22:29.240
Not bad!

22:29.240 --> 22:30.350
Make way!

22:35.310 --> 22:37.870
Where is Wen Chengye?

22:38.030 --> 22:38.790
I don't know.

22:38.790 --> 22:39.920
-Where did he go?
-Well done!

22:39.920 --> 22:40.960
Where is Wen Chengye?

22:40.960 --> 22:43.200
Seriously, where did Wen Chengye go?

22:43.200 --> 22:44.510
Interesting.

22:48.310 --> 22:49.640
Speed up!

22:51.440 --> 22:52.480
Come on, Boss!

22:52.850 --> 22:55.110
-It feels like flying!
-Congratulations, Ms. Lin.

22:55.110 --> 22:55.790
Watch out!

22:56.680 --> 22:58.200
You finally got 11 people.

23:01.440 --> 23:03.700
Congratulations to you too, Coach Wang.

23:07.000 --> 23:08.400
-Wait, wait!
-Stop arguing.

23:08.400 --> 23:09.440
Wait. Don't just...

23:09.440 --> 23:10.350
I'll go first.

23:10.370 --> 23:12.370
-Got it? I'll go first.
-Come on.

23:13.240 --> 23:14.440
Isn't this my bike?

23:15.440 --> 23:16.590
You little brats!

23:16.870 --> 23:17.920
You took my bike

23:17.920 --> 23:18.920
without my permission?

23:18.920 --> 23:19.880
I'll teach you a good lesson!

23:19.880 --> 23:21.680
-Wait!
-Th-That's Director Qian's bike!

23:21.680 --> 23:23.310
-Run!
-Run!

23:23.920 --> 23:24.830
-This way.
-What should we do?

23:24.830 --> 23:26.760
-I'm leaving now, bro.
-You brats!

23:27.960 --> 23:28.720
Sorry, Director!

23:28.720 --> 23:29.790
And you dropped my bike!

23:29.790 --> 23:31.200
-I'm sorry, Director!
-You brats!

23:31.200 --> 23:32.310
Let me explain!

23:33.160 --> 23:34.680
Lin Lu, just you wait!

23:34.680 --> 23:36.030
Stop! You little brats!

23:36.030 --> 23:37.330
Director, your bike has no brakes!

23:37.330 --> 23:38.400
Don't hit me!

23:39.510 --> 23:41.750
-Run!
-Run!

23:42.720 --> 23:44.270
Run faster!

23:44.270 --> 23:45.480
Lin Lu!

23:48.240 --> 23:50.370
You brat, stop right there!

23:51.550 --> 23:54.550
Could she, who would stand up
to protect her students,

23:54.830 --> 23:57.270
be Spade Q who killed Jason?

23:57.270 --> 23:58.960
I need to find a chance to verify it.

23:58.960 --> 24:01.160
-If you stop, I won't chase you!
-You've chased us for four laps!

24:01.160 --> 24:02.510
Watch your back!

24:08.350 --> 24:09.610
Good evening, Ms. Lin.

24:10.160 --> 24:11.160
Good evening.

24:11.160 --> 24:12.590
Is there something you need, Coach?

24:12.590 --> 24:14.030
I'm here to borrow a flashlight.

24:14.030 --> 24:14.890
Do you have one?

24:15.310 --> 24:16.830
I think so. Let me look.

24:21.520 --> 24:22.120
[Insect Extremes]

24:22.260 --> 24:23.490
[Curious] [Doesn't play by the rules]

24:23.510 --> 24:25.410
[Fireflies Expert]

24:28.880 --> 24:29.790
Found it.

24:29.790 --> 24:31.990
I didn't expect that I actually had one.

24:32.000 --> 24:32.510
Thanks.

24:33.240 --> 24:35.200
Dressed like this,

24:35.200 --> 24:37.000
are you going to
patrol the mountain tonight?

24:37.000 --> 24:38.070
Pretty much.

24:38.070 --> 24:39.400
Want to join me, Ms. Lin?

24:40.480 --> 24:41.830
I don't have the habit of doing

24:41.830 --> 24:43.720
high-intensity workouts late at night.

24:43.720 --> 24:44.990
I'm not going for a workout.

24:44.990 --> 24:46.520
I'm going to see fireflies.

24:46.680 --> 24:47.310
Thanks.

24:48.590 --> 24:49.680
Fireflies?

24:50.890 --> 24:51.680
Wait.

24:57.200 --> 24:57.930
What is this?

24:58.440 --> 25:00.070
Strong light will disturb them.

25:00.070 --> 25:02.070
Red light has less impact on them.

25:03.350 --> 25:06.070
Fireflies are usually active
from July to September.

25:06.070 --> 25:07.730
We can only try our luck today.

25:09.640 --> 25:11.240
The temperature is quite high this year.

25:11.240 --> 25:13.700
These two days
are their last active period.

25:14.550 --> 25:17.750
I didn't expect a great coach
to be interested in insects.

25:19.720 --> 25:20.590
Not really.

25:21.400 --> 25:23.160
I just occasionally encounter them
while hiking,

25:23.160 --> 25:24.760
so I learned a bit about them.

25:24.790 --> 25:27.190
I didn't expect him
to have so many hobbies.

25:28.680 --> 25:29.940
But...

25:30.200 --> 25:32.310
the sensible temperature
isn't that high today.

25:32.310 --> 25:34.270
Hope we won't end up with nothing.

25:35.750 --> 25:37.750
Aren't there cold-loving species?

25:38.070 --> 25:40.270
You mean Diaphanes citrinus?

25:43.400 --> 25:44.790
They are indeed cold-loving.

25:44.790 --> 25:47.070
But I don't know
if we can see them later.

25:48.830 --> 25:49.750
It seems you

25:49.750 --> 25:51.260
are a real insect lover.

25:51.960 --> 25:52.960
Not really.

25:52.960 --> 25:55.030
I just like fireflies.

25:57.200 --> 25:58.480
I got it wrong just now.

25:58.480 --> 26:00.680
I thought that small bulb was a firefly.

26:01.200 --> 26:02.550
I accidentally got too excited.

26:02.550 --> 26:03.400
Slow down.

26:05.000 --> 26:05.640
Sit here.

26:06.440 --> 26:07.270
Let me see.

26:24.070 --> 26:25.600
It should be no big problem.

26:25.960 --> 26:26.820
How do you feel?

26:27.310 --> 26:28.310
I'm fine.

26:28.310 --> 26:29.440
It's just a slight sprain.

26:29.440 --> 26:30.840
I'll be okay after a rest.

26:33.640 --> 26:35.480
Looks like we're out of luck today.

26:35.480 --> 26:37.210
We didn't see a single firefly.

26:38.640 --> 26:39.550
Let's wait a little longer.

26:39.550 --> 26:40.830
Maybe our luck will turn

26:40.830 --> 26:41.960
in a while.

26:50.030 --> 26:51.360
Do you know

26:52.110 --> 26:53.640
why I like fireflies?

26:59.110 --> 27:00.750
In junior high,

27:01.000 --> 27:02.930
my Chinese teacher told me

27:03.350 --> 27:04.830
that fireflies

27:04.920 --> 27:07.330
are amazing creatures.

27:08.720 --> 27:11.790
The light from a single firefly
is extremely faint,

27:12.680 --> 27:14.920
but when they gather together,

27:15.880 --> 27:17.940
they can light up the entire darkness

27:19.160 --> 27:21.560
and guide the way
for people walking ahead.

27:23.070 --> 27:25.100
They also use their faint light

27:25.400 --> 27:27.240
to define the value of life.

27:32.830 --> 27:35.110
I came to this school
to be a sports equipment keeper

27:35.110 --> 27:36.640
just to have an easier life.

27:36.920 --> 27:38.160
If you can,

27:38.160 --> 27:39.440
you can ease my burden

27:39.440 --> 27:40.790
and save my job.

27:47.480 --> 27:49.440
Why are you so calm?

27:49.440 --> 27:50.960
One team member is missing.

27:50.960 --> 27:53.240
I thought you'd already
handed the team over to me

27:53.240 --> 27:55.070
and stepped back
to let me handle everything.

27:55.070 --> 27:57.350
I'm their supervisor after all.

27:57.350 --> 27:59.810
I should at least
pay some attention to them.

28:05.070 --> 28:06.480
The cards in your hands

28:06.480 --> 28:09.540
contain the key points
for the monthly exam I prepared.

28:09.720 --> 28:11.640
I hope that from now on, every day

28:11.640 --> 28:12.720
and every moment,

28:12.720 --> 28:16.210
you will keep spelling words out loud
for Fu Xinshu to hear.

28:16.400 --> 28:18.510
Are you... Spade Q?

28:19.880 --> 28:21.160
The firefly effect

28:22.110 --> 28:25.240
was one of the concepts
I learned in my psychology class.

28:26.200 --> 28:28.000
Which one is the real you?

28:28.310 --> 28:30.160
So, from that moment on,

28:30.640 --> 28:33.400
I became
even more interested in fireflies.

28:34.310 --> 28:35.920
Who exactly are you?

28:37.880 --> 28:38.740
What about you?

28:40.880 --> 28:41.640
I...

28:43.560 --> 28:46.220
I just think
fireflies emitting their own light

28:46.400 --> 28:47.400
is quite special.

28:48.070 --> 28:49.670
I want to catch a few to study.

28:51.350 --> 28:52.550
Just because of that?

29:02.640 --> 29:03.880
Don't you think

29:05.000 --> 29:05.920
that Fu Xinshu

29:05.920 --> 29:06.920
is actually like

29:06.920 --> 29:08.590
a little firefly in the team?

29:09.480 --> 29:12.550
Even though he knows his power is small,

29:12.550 --> 29:14.920
he still tries hard to unite

29:14.920 --> 29:16.450
all the players on the team.

29:21.880 --> 29:22.680
What's wrong?

29:25.000 --> 29:26.000
Nothing.

29:27.550 --> 29:29.720
I just feel that you are

29:30.750 --> 29:32.680
quite different today from usual.

29:33.550 --> 29:35.150
You shared a lot of thoughts.

29:36.350 --> 29:37.590
That's because you've never

29:37.590 --> 29:39.190
really observed me closely.

29:44.640 --> 29:45.880
We've waited for ages

29:45.880 --> 29:47.810
and haven't seen a single firefly.

29:48.590 --> 29:49.650
It's getting late.

29:50.270 --> 29:51.160
Let's go.

29:52.270 --> 29:52.880
Your foot.

29:52.880 --> 29:53.310
Shh.

30:10.710 --> 30:13.030
♪ Two souls alike ♪

30:14.580 --> 30:16.460
♪ In the silent gravity ♪

30:18.730 --> 30:20.860
♪ Cure my heart ♪

30:20.440 --> 30:21.480
There really are fireflies.

30:21.480 --> 30:24.150
♪ With every part of you ♪

30:26.650 --> 30:28.730
♪ Our words flow ♪

30:30.120 --> 30:32.350
♪ Like a gentle stream ♪

30:34.440 --> 30:36.620
♪ They glow like fireflies ♪

30:37.280 --> 30:39.800
♪ Inside of a silky dream ♪

30:42.010 --> 30:47.840
♪ We talked the whole night, breeze away ♪

30:49.820 --> 30:51.610
♪ Together we set out on a long journey ♪

30:52.240 --> 30:55.300
♪ The endless journey ♪

30:58.030 --> 31:01.500
♪ Gently smoothing away ♪

31:01.960 --> 31:03.310
A writer once said,

31:02.230 --> 31:06.920
♪ The hesitation in each other's eyes ♪

31:03.920 --> 31:05.200
"Fireflies

31:05.200 --> 31:07.940
are love letters
written by the night to the earth."

31:07.940 --> 31:12.030
♪ Hearing the warmth inside ♪

31:08.270 --> 31:09.940
Compared to nature,

31:10.270 --> 31:12.130
humans are truly insignificant,

31:12.250 --> 31:13.250
aren't they?

31:13.710 --> 31:15.900
♪ Life begins alone ♪

31:16.830 --> 31:19.570
♪ A road we walk alone ♪

31:21.430 --> 31:23.720
♪ Until fate brings warmth ♪

31:24.450 --> 31:26.850
♪ To light our way back home ♪

31:30.090 --> 31:31.990
♪ True love is not just ♪

31:30.100 --> 31:31.700
Today

31:32.000 --> 31:33.350
was a happy day.

31:32.810 --> 31:34.270
♪ The first glance at the moment we met ♪

31:34.970 --> 31:37.910
♪ But the unwavering courage
when we hold each other close ♪

31:38.350 --> 31:40.030
It's because of the kids

31:40.920 --> 31:42.960
or that special galaxy?

31:46.510 --> 31:47.000
Both.

31:53.790 --> 31:54.400
By the way.

31:54.790 --> 31:57.240
It won't be long
before the match against Lyujing.

31:57.240 --> 31:59.170
Do you have any way to make them win?

32:01.750 --> 32:02.900
You want them...

32:02.950 --> 32:03.950
to win?

32:11.790 --> 32:12.990
If they beat Lyujing,

32:13.270 --> 32:15.330
they'll have to continue competing.

32:16.400 --> 32:17.240
Are you sure

32:17.240 --> 32:19.840
you want to be the Ms. Lin
who is forced to step up

32:20.550 --> 32:21.950
and stop being a slacker?

32:23.820 --> 32:25.150
How does that conflict?

32:25.350 --> 32:26.720
Since we have you, Coach,

32:26.720 --> 32:28.690
I can just keep being a slacker.

32:28.750 --> 32:30.280
Playing tricks won't work.

32:30.880 --> 32:32.740
This question is very important.

32:38.270 --> 32:40.130
My leg suddenly started hurting.

32:41.110 --> 32:43.570
Isn't it supposed
to be your head that hurts?

32:43.720 --> 32:45.000
I don't know.

32:45.000 --> 32:47.030
Thinking about the question you asked,

32:47.030 --> 32:48.110
my leg hurts more.

32:53.610 --> 32:54.400
Well,

32:55.310 --> 32:57.160
I'll give you, the one whose leg hurts,

32:57.160 --> 32:58.420
a day to think about it.

32:59.110 --> 33:00.590
There's no training tomorrow.

33:00.590 --> 33:01.750
After you get off work,

33:01.750 --> 33:04.410
I'll wait for your answer
at the lakeside trail.

33:07.400 --> 33:08.160
Answer?

33:09.000 --> 33:10.930
What answer could I possibly have?

33:29.960 --> 33:31.160
If they beat Lyujing,

33:31.410 --> 33:33.470
they'll have to continue competing.

33:34.440 --> 33:35.310
Are you sure

33:35.310 --> 33:37.910
you want to be the Ms. Lin
who is forced to step up

33:38.590 --> 33:39.990
and stop being a slacker?

33:42.730 --> 33:44.530
I'm just a team supervisor.

33:44.590 --> 33:46.050
Is that really the reason?

33:46.390 --> 33:47.200
Isn't it because,

33:47.200 --> 33:48.930
in your and Coach Wang's minds,

33:49.270 --> 33:51.350
the football team has always just been us,

33:51.350 --> 33:53.680
and there's no need
for you to be part of it?

33:54.000 --> 33:54.960
Answer?

33:56.240 --> 33:58.310
What answer could I possibly have?

34:13.670 --> 34:15.330
Aren't you here to run with me?

34:16.230 --> 34:17.480
My foot still hurts.

34:20.150 --> 34:22.409
Wearing high heels when your foot hurts?

34:22.880 --> 34:24.150
Have you made up your mind?

34:24.150 --> 34:24.960
I haven't.

34:26.800 --> 34:28.000
I want to be a slacker,

34:28.800 --> 34:30.260
and I also want them to win.

34:32.000 --> 34:32.880
Ms. Lin,

34:33.550 --> 34:35.800
you can't have your cake
and eat it too in life.

34:35.800 --> 34:37.150
Coach Wang Fa,

34:37.150 --> 34:40.280
life isn't always about
making quick decisions either.

34:40.880 --> 34:42.480
You must be hungry
after running for so long.

34:42.480 --> 34:43.030
Come on.

34:43.030 --> 34:45.030
I'll treat you to some rice noodles.

34:46.840 --> 34:48.110
Do you people who work out

34:48.110 --> 34:49.960
all cut carbs at night?

34:50.400 --> 34:51.320
Well...

34:53.920 --> 34:56.320
I'll bear the pain
and run with you for a bit.

35:17.440 --> 35:20.440
This is a small protest
against you not eating carbs.

35:26.960 --> 35:28.590
Sir, one grilled sausage.

35:28.590 --> 35:29.400
Alright.

35:29.920 --> 35:30.880
One iced Americano.

35:30.880 --> 35:32.140
Okay, one minute, sir.

35:40.480 --> 35:41.280
And this.

35:41.800 --> 35:42.480
Let me.

35:46.800 --> 35:47.960
Thanks, Coach Wang.

35:50.670 --> 35:51.470
Wait a moment.

35:51.710 --> 35:52.310
Thank you.

35:53.880 --> 35:54.840
Thank you.

36:00.710 --> 36:01.800
You're here?

36:05.400 --> 36:06.230
Have some.

36:11.920 --> 36:13.190
Don't scare it.

36:14.190 --> 36:15.320
Come on, eat up here.

36:18.670 --> 36:19.670
Here.

36:24.030 --> 36:25.070
It's a good chance

36:25.070 --> 36:26.400
to help those boys.

36:27.920 --> 36:29.920
Isn't it cute?

36:32.430 --> 36:34.030
Let me use this opportunity.

36:34.670 --> 36:36.110
Don't you think

36:36.110 --> 36:37.520
those football boys

36:37.840 --> 36:39.510
are as cute as this dog?

36:40.440 --> 36:42.510
But as their team supervisor,

36:43.110 --> 36:44.400
you look very distressed.

36:44.400 --> 36:46.280
Isn't it because of you?

36:46.880 --> 36:48.670
Are you willing to help or not?

36:48.670 --> 36:49.710
You said yourself

36:49.710 --> 36:50.910
that you're worth it.

36:53.000 --> 36:54.260
Going round and round,

36:54.710 --> 36:56.710
you're back to reverse psychology.

36:57.480 --> 36:59.320
Stubborn as a mule.

37:04.960 --> 37:05.880
I got an idea.

37:06.670 --> 37:07.760
How about this?

37:07.760 --> 37:09.190
To be fair,

37:09.190 --> 37:11.070
let's each offer it some freeze-dried food

37:11.070 --> 37:12.110
and see

37:12.110 --> 37:13.400
who it takes it from.

37:13.420 --> 37:15.280
We'll go with whoever it chooses.

37:16.670 --> 37:17.230
Sure.

37:19.030 --> 37:19.710
Here.

37:24.760 --> 37:25.630
Doggy.

37:27.510 --> 37:28.510
Doggy, doggy.

37:32.750 --> 37:34.070
Doggy, come.

37:35.000 --> 37:36.320
It ate it.

37:36.320 --> 37:37.480
See?

37:39.800 --> 37:41.590
It's destiny.

37:41.590 --> 37:43.070
I won.

37:43.070 --> 37:45.800
Looking forward to working with you,
Coach Wang.

37:46.480 --> 37:47.880
Let me see.

37:48.840 --> 37:50.140
I suspect

37:51.070 --> 37:53.630
you're a helper Ms. Lin brought in

37:53.630 --> 37:54.800
to make me lose.

37:59.960 --> 38:01.560
What's wrong with your hand?

38:02.480 --> 38:03.590
It looks injured.

38:05.360 --> 38:05.880
It's fine.

38:05.880 --> 38:06.880
It's not fine.

38:06.880 --> 38:08.510
This looks serious.

38:08.510 --> 38:09.210
Let's go to my place.

38:09.210 --> 38:10.410
I'll treat it for you.

38:10.960 --> 38:11.360
Let's go.

38:11.360 --> 38:12.840
Is she...

38:12.870 --> 38:14.430
worried about me?

38:22.070 --> 38:22.920
Does it hurt?

38:24.400 --> 38:25.230
Not too bad.

38:29.710 --> 38:31.080
Actually,

38:31.230 --> 38:32.920
the puppy downstairs—

38:32.920 --> 38:34.800
even though I've never fed it—

38:35.190 --> 38:36.400
really likes me.

38:36.800 --> 38:38.330
It always acts cute with me.

38:38.920 --> 38:40.000
I already guessed

38:40.000 --> 38:42.000
that it would definitely choose me.

38:42.030 --> 38:42.880
I know.

38:43.920 --> 38:45.030
You know?

38:45.590 --> 38:47.550
Then why didn't you expose me right there?

38:47.550 --> 38:49.280
That's not Coach Wang's style.

38:50.150 --> 38:52.150
Then should I pull up my payment QR code

38:52.150 --> 38:54.480
and charge you for being such a gentleman?

38:57.230 --> 38:59.630
I have something more valuable than that.

39:01.800 --> 39:02.600
Sit over here.

39:12.710 --> 39:15.400
These are the latest
aromatherapy diffusers and candles.

39:15.400 --> 39:18.200
They can relieve your insomnia
more effectively.

39:23.070 --> 39:23.920
Feel it out.

39:24.760 --> 39:26.820
Do you prefer the ocean or the forest?

39:29.550 --> 39:30.320
The ocean.

39:32.590 --> 39:34.400
This is the white noise of the ocean.

39:34.400 --> 39:36.320
Next, I want to teach you

39:36.320 --> 39:37.510
some meditation techniques

39:37.510 --> 39:39.240
that can help you sleep better.

39:39.630 --> 39:40.550
Follow me.

39:41.670 --> 39:42.920
First,

39:42.920 --> 39:44.320
relax your body and mind.

39:47.190 --> 39:48.550
Close your eyes.

39:50.670 --> 39:52.190
Take a deep breath.

39:52.190 --> 39:53.440
Inhale.

39:55.360 --> 39:56.590
Exhale.

40:03.400 --> 40:04.590
Imagine that

40:05.070 --> 40:06.480
in front of you

40:06.480 --> 40:09.590
is a vast, boundless ocean.

40:10.280 --> 40:12.360
In this space,

40:12.360 --> 40:14.510
there is only the ocean and you.

40:15.510 --> 40:18.510
You are far away
from the hustle and bustle of the city.

40:19.510 --> 40:22.000
You sway with the waves,

40:22.000 --> 40:25.800
swaying, swaying, swaying.

41:01.070 --> 41:04.200
Not answering the phone
this early in the morning again.

41:04.480 --> 41:05.480
Unbelievable.

41:29.360 --> 41:31.490
Your expression right now is so gross.

41:32.430 --> 41:33.480
It's not, is it?

41:34.280 --> 41:36.550
I'm just happy for my bro.

41:37.670 --> 41:38.760
-Unbelievable.
-Right?

41:38.760 --> 41:39.840
Give me back my house keys.

41:39.840 --> 41:40.320
No.

41:43.840 --> 41:45.440
Did you go there this morning or last...

41:45.440 --> 41:47.000
Why are you so gossipy?

41:48.110 --> 41:50.360
Can we only talk about business?

41:50.920 --> 41:53.030
I don't have time for this. Open the door.

41:53.030 --> 41:54.000
Why did you take

41:54.000 --> 41:54.880
my house keys?

41:54.880 --> 41:57.540
What do you think?
How would you live without me?

42:08.140 --> 42:09.460
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

42:10.550 --> 42:12.040
♪ Because you're with me ♪

42:14.790 --> 42:16.230
♪ The light shimmers ♪

42:17.490 --> 42:18.810
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪

42:20.390 --> 42:21.510
♪ Running towards you ♪

42:22.420 --> 42:23.680
♪ I keep moving fearlessly ♪

42:27.460 --> 42:28.700
♪ Walk side by side ♪

42:29.260 --> 42:31.390
♪ Become ourselves ♪

42:33.170 --> 42:34.750
♪ We get closer in a storm ♪
